snippet.title: Monster Match Trailer
snippet.description:
Monster Match is a fast-paced, match-3 style puzzle game! You are a Lich who's castle is under attack by some heroes!

Match monster essences to summon monsters to fight your foes and keep them from advancing on your lair!

Available NOW for Windows on Itch.io!

https://axolstudio.itch.io/monster-match

©2019 Axol Studio, LLC
axolstudio.com
